{"image_id": "PNR_2015_page_95", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Pentair plc and Subsidiaries", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 405.1, 179.7]}, {"text": "Notes to consolidated financial statements", "bbox": [162.5, 183.9, 524.0, 204.7]}, {"text": "Gains or losses on foreign currency contracts designated as hedges are reclassified out of AOCI and into Selling,", "bbox": [162.5, 233.9, 1112.4, 254.9]}, {"text": "general and administrative expense in the Consolidated Statements of Operations and Comprehensive Income", "bbox": [162.5, 258.9, 1112.4, 279.9]}, {"text": "(Loss) upon settlement. Such reclassifications during 2015, 2014 and 2013 were not material.", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 943.0, 304.9]}, {"text": "Net investment hedge", "bbox": [162.5, 329.8, 340.9, 350.6]}, {"text": "We have net investments in foreign subsidiaries that are subject to changes in the foreign currency exchange rate.", "bbox": [162.5, 355.0, 1112.4, 375.8]}, {"text": "In September 2015, we designated the €500 million 2.45% Senior Notes due 2019 (the “2019 Euro Notes”) as a", "bbox": [162.5, 379.2, 1112.5, 400.8]}, {"text": "net investment hedge for a portion of our net investment in our Euro denominated subsidiaries. The gains/losses", "bbox": [162.5, 405.0, 1112.3, 425.8]}, {"text": "on the 2019 Euro Notes have been included as a component of the cumulative translation adjustment account", "bbox": [162.5, 430.0, 1112.4, 450.8]}, {"text": "within AOCI. As of December 31, 2015, we had deferred foreign currency gains of $16.4 million in AOCI", "bbox": [162.5, 455.0, 1112.6, 475.8]}, {"text": "associated with the net investment hedge activity.", "bbox": [162.5, 480.0, 576.9, 500.8]}, {"text": "Fair value of financial instruments", "bbox": [162.5, 525.7, 464.9, 546.6]}, {"text": "The following methods were used to estimate the fair values of each class of financial instrument:", "bbox": [162.5, 550.9, 979.2, 571.8]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [200.0, 586.4, 207.3, 607.2]}, {"text": "short-term financial instruments (cash and cash equivalents, accounts and notes receivable, accounts and", "bbox": [237.5, 586.4, 1112.5, 607.2]}, {"text": "notes payable and variable-rate debt) — recorded amount approximates fair value because of the short", "bbox": [237.5, 611.4, 1112.4, 632.2]}, {"text": "maturity period;", "bbox": [237.5, 636.4, 372.6, 657.2]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [200.0, 671.8, 207.3, 692.6]}, {"text": "long-term fixed-rate debt, including current maturities — fair value is based on market quotes available", "bbox": [237.5, 671.8, 1112.3, 692.6]}, {"text": "for issuance of debt with similar terms, which are inputs that are classified as Level 2 in the valuation", "bbox": [237.5, 696.8, 1112.3, 717.6]}, {"text": "hierarchy defined by the accounting guidance; and", "bbox": [237.5, 721.8, 659.4, 742.6]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [200.0, 757.2, 207.3, 778.0]}, {"text": "foreign currency contract agreements — fair values are determined through the use of models that", "bbox": [237.5, 757.2, 1112.4, 778.0]}, {"text": "consider various assumptions, including time value, yield curves, as well as other relevant economic", "bbox": [237.5, 782.2, 1112.4, 803.0]}, {"text": "measures, which are inputs that are classified as Level 2 in the valuation hierarchy defined by the", "bbox": [237.5, 807.2, 1112.4, 828.0]}, {"text": "accounting guidance.", "bbox": [237.5, 832.2, 414.7, 853.0]}, {"text": "The recorded amounts and estimated fair values of total debt at December 31 were as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 878.1, 947.8, 899.0]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [768.8, 919.7, 810.4, 940.5]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [992.7, 919.7, 1034.4, 940.5]}, {"text": "In millions", "bbox": [162.5, 969.7, 252.2, 990.5]}, {"text": "Recorded", "bbox": [689.5, 948.9, 775.1, 969.7]}, {"text": "Amount", "bbox": [695.8, 969.7, 768.7, 990.5]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [827.7, 948.9, 865.9, 969.7]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [820.8, 969.7, 872.9, 990.5]}, {"text": "Recorded", "bbox": [916.0, 948.9, 100